The ahtimeconv tool converts a single time between various time systems 
and formats.  Supported systems: Mission-Elapsed Time (MET), Terrestrial
Time (TT), and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).  Supported formats are
seconds elapsed since epoch, days elapsed since epoch, Julian Day (JD),
Modified Julian Day (MJD), YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.xxxx, and 
YYYY-DDDThh:mm:ss.xxxx.
